title: Hallmark-When Calls The Heart [2013]
description:
Hallmark-When Calls the Heart (2013) 

Air Date: 19 Oct 2013

Summary: Elizabeth Thatcher, a cultured young teacher in 1910, fears leaving her comfortable world in the city. But when she accepts a teaching position in a frontier town, she finds new purpose and love with a handsome Royal Canadian Mountie.
